---

This project is a Swift port of SurGe (https://github.com/karimknaebel/surge).
The SurGe source code is released under the MIT License. The SurGe model
weights are released under CC BY-NC 4.0 and are NOT distributed with this
repository — users download them separately from Hugging Face
(karimknaebel/surge-large) and remain subject to that license. SurGe builds on
MoGe (https://github.com/microsoft/MoGe); the DINOv2 encoder and geometry
utilities here follow the mlx-swift-MoGe port.
